title: Dropbox hikes IPO price range
text:
Dropbox hikes IPO price range 10:57am EDT - 00:48 
Dropbox, the first big tech IPO of this year, raised its price range by $2. As Fred Katayama reports, that suggests the cloud storage firm will be valued at up to nearly $8 billion. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
